sql:
SELECT AVG(game_length) AS avg_game_length
FROM matches
WHERE game_mode = 'Ranked';

SELECT match_id, total_damage_dealt_to_champions
FROM teams
WHERE team_early_surrendered = 1 AND aces_before_15_minutes = 1;

external_knowledge:
- A surrendered game is one where the losing team concedes defeat before the match is completed; 
- 300 seconds is equivalent to 5 minutes; 
- A Baron kill is when a team kills the powerful Baron Nashor, a neutral computer-controlled monster in the game.

